OL,3,CThird British national diagnosed with
OL,4,Csuspected hantavirus linked to cruise
OL,5,Cship
OL,7,FA third British national has been
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with suspected hantavirus
OL,9,Flinked to a cruise ship outbreak,
OL,10,Fhealth officials have said.
OL,12,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,13,Fsaid two British nationals have
OL,14,Fconfirmed hantavirus but there is now
OL,15,F"an additional suspected case of a
OL,16,FBritish national on Tristan da Cunha".
OL,18,FThe patient remains on the remote
OL,19,FSouth Atlantic island.
