OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778256666
OL,3,CThird British national diagnosed with
OL,4,Csuspected hantavirus linked to cruise
OL,5,Cship
OL,7,FThree people have died following the
OL,8,Foutbreak, which Argentine officials
OL,9,Fsuspect occurred when a Dutch couple
OL,10,Fcame in contact with the virus on a
OL,11,Fbird-watching trip in the country.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, World Health
OL,14,FOrganisation (WHO) officals said three
OL,15,Fsuspected hantavirus patients had been
OL,16,Fevacuated from the ship and flown to
OL,17,Freceive specialist medical care in the
OL,18,FNetherlands.
